organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: No. 2 Syracuse won at Rutgers, 74-64, as C. J. Fair scored a career-high 21 points and Scoop Jardine added 17, including a game-sealing 3-pointer with 1 minute 11 seconds left.
